      {"text": "The application code for the /health endpoint has a bug", "feedback": "Incorrect. If health endpoint returns 200 when tested directly, the endpoint code is fine."},
      {"text": "The load balancer needs to be restarted to clear its health check cache", "feedback": "Incorrect. LB health checks are real-time — there's no cache to clear."},
